-- Development Bank of Japan Hires Three Banks for Bond Sale
-- B y   Y u s u k e   M i y a z a w a
-- 2012-05-15T00:14:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-15/development-bank-of-japan-hires-three-banks-for-bond-sale.html
Development  Bank of Japan (8301)  hired
Nomura Holdings Inc., Daiwa Securities Group Inc. and  Mizuho
Financial Group Inc. (8411)  for a sale of three- and five-year bonds,
according to an e-mailed statement from Nomura.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yusuke Miyazawa in Tokyo at 
